title: The Abbott and Costello Show Seasons 1, 2
description:
Bud and Lou are unemployed actors living in Mr. Fields' boarding house. Lou's girlfriend Hillary lives across the hall. Any premise would lead to slapstick, puns, lots of gimmicks from their movies.

This is not a complete listing of all the shows but only what could be found on TPB and KT. Some shows were a partial download, but most of the show works, so I included them.

All shows are renamed for PLEX server identification from TVdb.com
